{"tid":677732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真post) 破處一問","createTime":"2018-05-25T12:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T15:51:12.000Z","uid":88527,"like":6,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"47a165832e378c077d94af6c2ea5b8cd89b7d2d1","tid":677732,"uid":88527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"我係女<br />\n同男朋友long d<br />\n我去咗搵佢 所以最近都一齊住<br />\n佢都幾大食 我日日都要幫佢含&gt;1次 好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係處黎佢唔係 不過我都預咗遲早都俾佢<br />\n佢開到口話想要 所以我地差唔多日日都試<br />\n但入到少少我就已經覺得好痛<br />\n痛到唔想再搞 完全冇mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋男朋友成日唔想帶套入<br />\n係咁話帶套好難入 佢完全feel唔到個窿係邊<br />\n不過佢都有聽我講 好唔情願咁帶套試入<br />\n<br />\n但係帶親套 佢好辛苦咁<br />\n個套勁緊 帶完之後好又易唔硬<br />\n我等得黎又唔濕<br />\n佢再試入 我又好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁試 痛咗好多次<br />\n我開始好驚佢入<br />\n啱啱又係fail<br />\n我同佢講好痛 我唔想呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就話 唔搞囉<br />\n然後我地冇講過野<br />\n<br />\n我feel到佢唔開心<br />\n但我因爲咁更唔開心<br />\n點解佢要逼我做d我唔想做既野<br />\n佢似愛性&gt;愛我<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以開解下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640deb5e750595186c85ddd7e153e2bef43da5ab","tid":677732,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"唔戴套小心生性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb5790043046909df06b0ce98e4f2c93676187d","tid":677732,"uid":2546,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"睇黎佢淨係想要你個處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830d26e3167557c4786b0bfa0d4227b1fb50c641","tid":677732,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"扑完你再扑其他女"},{"pid":"69271658f9e71